audio_descriptions.notes:
A grassy traffic island in the middle of a small highway. The traffic island has a lawn chair, a grill, and a cooler. There is a True Value in the background.
Dad enters and sits in the lawn chair.
Dad loosens his tie, takes off his shoes, and puts his feet up on the cooler. 
-Dad opens the grill, revealing a can of FOOD. He looks at the can of FOOD and closes the grill. Cars periodically drive by on the highway lane behind him.
-Dad puts his hands behind his head, smiling.
-Dad rubs his feet, rotating his ankles, before putting them back up on the cooler.
Dad slowly looks around, smiling.
[3:43] Dad picks up his shoes, clapping the soles together, and puts them back down. 
He opens the grill, looking at the can of FOOD inside. 
Dad licks his lips and rubs his stomach.
He closes the grill again.
[5:03] Dad waves at someone offscreen, smiling.
[6:03] Dad turns around and looks at the True Value.
He smiles, gesturing at the True Value, and turns back around.
[6:19] Dad opens the grill and looks at the can of FOOD. 
He opens the cooler, pulling out a red thermos and drinking from it. 
He closes the cooler with his foot and puts his feet back up on it.
He continues to drink from the thermos periodically.
[7:00] Dad waves at someone offscreen.
[7:35] Dad touches the can of FOOD gingerly, as though it's hot, and adjusts it slightly on the grill. 
He closes the grill, patting it affectionately.
[9:00] Dad sits up, leaning forward and squinting at something offscreen. He looks at it curiously before settling back in his chair, relaxed and smiling.
[9:45 ish] Dad rubs his bald head.
[11:00] Dad stretches, putting his hands behind his head.
Dad closes his eyes. He seems to drift off to sleep.
[11:42] A brief shot of a woman with short dark hair and a man that looks like Dad, but with hair. They sit together outdoors, small lamps glowing gently around them.
Dad stirs and wakes up.
Dad checks on the FOOD.
He rests his thermos on top of the grill. 
Dad yawns. He seems to drift back off to sleep.
[13:25] A brief shot of the short-haired woman, looking up. There are leaves and pink flowers behind her.
Dad stirs and wakes up. A man in a car drives up to Dad and stops. Dad waves at the man. The man smiles and drives away.
Dad yawns and drifts back off to sleep.
[14:30] Dad wakes up. He sits up, still looking sleepy.
[15:30] Dad yawns. He pats his stomach, then takes a drink from his thermos.
Dad looks around and smiles, periodically drinking from his thermos.
[17:40] Dad turns around and looks at the True Value, smiling.
[19:45] Dad turns and looks at the grill. He cleans a spot of it with his tie.
[20:10] Dad pats the grill and smiles.
He turns, looking at someone off screen. He gestures at the grill and then at himself, smiling. He waves a hand dismissively and laughs.
Dad opens the grill to check the food.
Dad settles back into his chair. 
He waves at someone offscreen.
[22:00] Dad looks incredulously as a skateboarder moves along the edge of the road. He scoffs and waves him off dismissively.
[23:05] Dad seems to finish the drink from his thermos. He puts it on his cooler. He opens the grill, looking at the can of FOOD. He pulls the the lid off his thermos and picks up the FOOD, holding it gingerly as though it's hot. 
He pours red liquid from the can into his thermos. 
He blows on the liquid and drinks from the thermos.
 He puts the can back on the grill and closes it. 
He puts the lid back on his thermos and continues to drink from it.

24:45- Dad yawns.
26:15: Dad watches admiringly as a minivan drives by.
30:00 Dad untucks his shirt and shakes it out slightly.
30:22 A man dressed in black walks past the True Value. He stops at a nearby tree and stands there, unmoving. He is faced toward Dad.
31:30 The man in black walks away.
32:45 Dad mimes revving a motorcycle and smiles.
34:00- A man jogs across the street. Dad waves at him as he passes.
36:50- Dad seems to fall asleep.
40:20- A brief shot of the short-haired woman looking over her shoulder. Dad wakes up.

43:20- Dad opens the grill. 
He smells the can of FOOD. 
He takes the FOOD off the grill.
He refills his thermos with the red liquid in the FOOD can.
He puts the FOOD can on top of the grill. He continues to drink from his thermos.
45:20- Dad dances slightly in his seat. He rubs his bald head.
46:40- Dad undoes his tie. He stretches.
50:00- Dad waves at someone offscreen.
51:00- Dad puts down his thermos.
He pats his stomach contentedly.
52:20- Dad's FOOD can falls off of his grill. Dad seems surprised. 
He picks up the can and brushes it off. 
He puts the can and his thermos in his cooler.
55:50- Dad rubs his eyes.
59:45- Dad shields his eyes, looking at something off-camera.
1:00:18- The short haired woman briefly appears onscreen. Dad then seems to fall asleep. 
The woman appears again and looks directly at the camera. When she speaks, her lips do not move
1:00:30- A man in a red vest comes out of the True Value. He is holding something. He stops and looks at Dad, unmoving.
1:00:45- The man in the red vest leaves.
1:01:32- The man in the red vest walks up to Dad on the traffic island. We can now see that it is Crothers. He is holding a wrapped present shaped like a sledgehammer. He kneels down next to Dad, who wakes up.
1:02:05 Crothers gives Dad the present.
Crothers leaves. Dad looks down at the present, confused.
Dad looks at the camera in confusion.
Cut to black.
End card shows Dad standing next to the True Value, looking up at its sign. There is text reading, "What is Dad's gift?" There are video links to "True Value" and "True Value Lyric Video".
